{"title":"ATB Patologias ORL","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología/ATB Patologias ORL iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"ANTIBIOTICOS EN\\NPATOLOGIAS ORL","guid":"78F2BqpZYuN50uDH3jTf_Q","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"MICROBIOLOGIA\\NGENERAL","guid":"R2UPQ7KzADVOKpXR5rBc0A","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Patogenos principales\\Nvias aereas superiores","guid":"6Rp9s-S8A8jyV5N3tZIsFA","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"S. pneumoniae → MAS FRECUENTE\\Nen sinusitis y OMA","guid":"qGfqHmL4jc40RGsUtmTXXQ","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"Resistencia a macrolidos ~30% → NO usar azitro empirica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"Resistencia a TMP/SMX ~30-40%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"3","text":"Sensibilidad conservada a amoxicilina dosis altas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"2","text":"H. influenzae →\\Nbeta-lactamasa (+)\\N27-43%","guid":"8B4iyQIKPkSEQ07kTTleLA","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Amoxicilina sola puede fallar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Amoxi/clav cubre cepas productoras","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"2","text":"M. catarrhalis → >90%\\Nproduce beta-lactamasa","guid":"X7ybdc-iIB4dYhY2wHMm9w","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"Habitualmente autolimitada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"Responde a amoxi/clav, cefalosporinas, quinolonas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"2","text":"S. pyogenes (SBHGA) →\\NPRINCIPAL en faringitis bacteriana","guid":"QHM587fSL70athUVk63v6A","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"100% sensible a penicilina (sin resistencia descrita)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"Resistencia creciente a macrolidos y clindamicina","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"2","text":"Anaerobios (Fusobacterium,\\NPrevotella, Peptostreptococcus)","guid":"LkcD_VM6x6jct07aeCEusA","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"Relevantes en infecciones profundas de cuello","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"Flegmon/absceso periamigdalino","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"Angina de Vincent","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"16","text":"Cubrir con metronidazol o amoxi/clav","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"RINOSINUSITIS AGUDA\\NBACTERIANA (RSAB)","guid":"3KVqIMensB0g--N4y1U5kQ","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Diagnostico clinico\\N(IDSA 2012 /\\NAAO-HNS 2015)","guid":"r_GEaAHNABJrig9P1O2qbw","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Sintomas >=10 dias sin mejoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"Inicio severo: fiebre >=39C + descarga purulenta >=3-4 dias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"Empeoramiento tras mejoria inicial (doble enfermamiento)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"21","text":"PRIMERA LINEA →\\NAmoxicilina/Acido clavulanico","guid":"aRD4IsTb0VkzMbWYPjI7RA","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Dosis estandar: 875/125 mg c/12h x 5-7 dias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Dosis alta: 2g/125mg c/12h\\N(si sospecha neumococo\\Nresistente)","guid":"_0m8fYQ515QaPjZb05EahA","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Indicaciones\\Ndosis alta","guid":"67ArSb682Wu96hrE2cud1A","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Region con >=10% S. pneumoniae no susceptible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"Infeccion severa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"Edad >65 anos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"29","text":"Hospitalizacion reciente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"29","text":"ATB ultimo mes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"29","text":"Inmunocomprometido","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"21","text":"ALERGIA A\\NPENICILINA","guid":"XAQQcxhUYnb5BS6xP_veGQ","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Tipo 1 (anafilaxia, urticaria, angioedema)\\N→ EVITAR betalactamicos","guid":"g9iWInEmR1Las-rUvTXs8Q","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Doxiciclina 100mg c/12h x 5-7 dias (IDSA: recomendacion fuerte)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"Levofloxacino 500mg/dia x 5-7 dias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"Moxifloxacino 400mg/dia x 5-7 dias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"PRECAUCION\\Nfluoroquinolonas","guid":"qvXf_NjeUfM1RZA42CCesA","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"FDA 2016: riesgo > beneficio en sinusitis no complicada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Reservar para sin alternativa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Riesgo tendinopatia → ESPECIAL ATENCION en adulto mayor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"QT prolongado, convulsiones, neuropatia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"37","text":"Costo\\Nen Chile","guid":"feym9cWr99vacHMW1Fmwbw","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Levofloxacino/Moxifloxacino → ACCESIBLES","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Cefuroxima/Cefpodoxima → ~$60.000/caja → BARRERA ECONOMICA","guid":"BnpicS1Re5LCMI1Zf98wmw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"36","text":"Tipo NO 1 (rash tardio,\\Nintolerancia GI)","guid":"2CoMA3jI5aCZQKGnBAmAcw","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"Cefalosporinas 2a-3a gen son SEGURAS","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"Cefuroxima axetilo 500mg c/12h x 5-7 dias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"Cefpodoxima 200mg c/12h","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"36","text":"NO USAR como\\Nprimera linea","guid":"HI2yZHLzMvrKcHGfbPqSYw","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Azitromicina → resistencia neumococica ~30%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"TMP/SMX → resistencia ~30-40%","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"21","text":"FALLA TERAPEUTICA\\N(sin mejoria 3-5 dias)","guid":"xL7263IlFUtVZPSmFEbKfw","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Si inicio con observacion → iniciar ATB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"Si inicio con amoxicilina → cambiar a amoxi/clav dosis alta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"Si inicio con amoxi/clav → fluoroquinolona respiratoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"56","text":"Considerar cultivo por puncion sinusal o endoscopia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"21","text":"Tratamiento adyuvante","guid":"","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Corticoide intranasal (Avamys, mometasona)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Lavado nasal con solucion salina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"AINE x 3 dias si dolor intenso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"Antihistaminico solo si componente alergico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"0","text":"RINOSINUSITIS CRONICA\\N(>12 semanas)","guid":"VFZ8do69q9WeMlFDTxq5MA","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Sin polipos\\N(RSCsP)","guid":"q-9mAR1oZAmp5tyjbne6xg","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"ATB prolongados si reagudizacion bacteriana","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"MACROLIDO A DOSIS BAJA PROLONGADA\\N→ efecto INMUNOMODULADOR","guid":"fb8ZAjXemYD0TWHFMxcOCQ","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"Azitromicina 250mg 3 veces/semana x 12-24 semanas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"Mecanismo: reduce IL-8, neutrofilos, biofilm","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"Mismo principio que en bronquiectasias y panbronquiolitis difusa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"69","text":"NO es efecto antibiotico → es antiinflamatorio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"67","text":"Cultivo guiado por endoscopia si refractaria","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"66","text":"Con polipos\\N(RSCcP)","guid":"RjI5xaZVYU0DFfDt1COdsg","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Inflamacion predominante Th2/eosinofilica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Corticoides topicos → PILAR del tratamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"Corticoides sistemicos en reagudizaciones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"Cirugia endoscopica funcional (FESS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"75","text":"Biologicos: dupilumab, omalizumab, mepolizumab","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"75","text":"ATB solo en sobreinfeccion documentada","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"0","text":"OTITIS MEDIA\\NAGUDA\\N(OMA)","guid":"bp8jeIkzc-xf7_YyZhTzDA","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"85% autoresolucion → considerar observacion expectante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"Primera linea → Amoxicilina 80-90mg/kg/dia (ninos) o 1g c/8h (adultos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"Falla o severa → Amoxi/clav dosis alta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"82","text":"Alergia\\Npenicilina","guid":"rxbD8klpS871asjTVp5QKg","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"No tipo 1 → cefalosporina (cefuroxima, ceftriaxona IM)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"Tipo 1 → TMP/SMX o azitromicina (segunda linea)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"Clindamicina si sospecha neumococo resistente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"82","text":"OMA recurrente → NO usar ATB profilactico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"82","text":"Adulto con OMA unilateral persistente >2 meses → DESCARTAR tumor nasofaringeo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"0","text":"OTITIS\\NEXTERNA","guid":"hOL72EQIIVLf00qqCNCiTw","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"Aguda difusa\\N(oido de nadador)","guid":"sv0U7XQ9_yKgssmZbQPerw","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"Pseudomonas aeruginosa y S. aureus","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"Gotas oticas con ciprofloxacino + dexametasona","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"93","text":"ATB sistemico solo si celulitis periauricular o fiebre","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"92","text":"Maligna/necrotizante\\N→ EMERGENCIA","guid":"MY_iloxNoJJdeagoIhK42Q","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Pseudomonas aeruginosa casi siempre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"Adulto mayor + diabetes → SOSPECHA CLINICA ALTA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"Ciprofloxacino IV + anti-Pseudomonas (ceftazidima o piperacilina/tazo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"97","text":"Larga duracion (6-8 semanas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"97","text":"Imagen: TC temporal + gammagrafia con Tc99/Ga67","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"0","text":"FARINGITIS /\\NAMIGDALITIS","guid":"ZXP2cNtH6Zqm7h5xjlq9CQ","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"Viral (>80%) → NO ATB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"SBHGA (5-15% adultos) → confirmar con test rapido o cultivo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"Criterios de Centor/McIsaac para orientar estudio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"103","text":"Primera linea →\\NPenicilina V o\\NAmoxicilina x 10 dias","guid":"HzWaNn21Dccg9R_NFBIB2g","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"Amoxicilina 1g c/12h (adultos) o 50mg/kg/dia (ninos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"107","text":"Penicilina benzatina 1.2M UI IM dosis unica (si mala adherencia)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"103","text":"Alergia\\Npenicilina","guid":"gfF6YOtTm9hdSMk5u_0fdw","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"No tipo 1 → cefalosporina 1a gen\\N(cefalexina 500mg c/12h x 10d)","guid":"dDoV4Eoz3daOwu-Wk4Xqnw","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"PRECAUCION: cefalexina tiene cadena R1 similar a amoxicilina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"111","text":"Si anafilaxia a amoxicilina → NO usar cefalexina","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"110","text":"Tipo 1 → clindamicina 300mg c/8h x 10d","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"110","text":"Tipo 1 → azitromicina 500mg dia 1, luego 250mg x 4 dias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"Resistencia creciente de SBHGA a macrolidos → vigilar","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"103","text":"NO usar fluoroquinolonas en faringitis → espectro innecesariamente amplio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"103","text":"NO usar TMP/SMX → no erradica SBHGA","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"0","text":"INFECCIONES\\NPROFUNDAS DE\\NCUELLO","guid":"UEtFZAj9h1Fb8TigSJlL-A","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"Flegmon/absceso\\Nperiamigdalino","guid":"2pxo5M-x2-gjpm67r5SBhQ","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"Flora polimicrobiana: SBHGA + anaerobios","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"Leve → Amoxi/clav 875/125 c/12h + metronidazol 500mg c/8h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":"Severo →\\Nhospitalizar","guid":"wqMwKBUficmgz1mNmRtobg","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"Ampicilina/sulbactam IV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"Alternativa: clindamicina IV (cubre aerobios y anaerobios)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"123","text":"Ceftriaxona + metronidazol","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"120","text":"Drenaje si absceso formado","guid":"oHOsis-kGNli8MN-BCRB1Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"119","text":"Absceso retrofaringeo /\\Nparafaringeo","guid":"_a6ihaafCMdVP2VhVljxcQ","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"EMERGENCIA → via aerea comprometida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"TC cuello con contraste","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"ATB IV amplio espectro + drenaje quirurgico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"128","text":"Amoxi/clav IV o Ampicilina/sulbactam","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"128","text":"Alternativa: ceftriaxona + metronidazol","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"119","text":"Angina de\\NLudwig","guid":"-r3Mo5PiJ-POPxZwSTqxkg","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"Piso de boca, origen odontogenico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"Via aerea → PRIORIDAD ABSOLUTA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"ATB IV: Ampicilina/sulbactam o Penicilina G + metronidazol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"134","text":"Drenaje quirurgico temprano","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"119","text":"Sindrome de Lemierre\\N(tromboflebitis yugular septica)","guid":"izRk49Lis4w5O8SzK6_I5A","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Fusobacterium necrophorum","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"ATB: metronidazol + cefalosporina 3a gen","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"Anticoagulacion → controversial","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"0","text":"EPIGLOTITIS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"Adultos → H. influenzae, SBHGA, S. pneumoniae, S. aureus","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"EMERGENCIA → manejo de via aerea primero","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"ATB IV: ceftriaxona 2g/dia o cefotaxima","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"143","text":"Alternativa: ampicilina/sulbactam","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"143","text":"Agregar vancomicina si sospecha SAMR","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES\\NGERIATRICAS\\N(TRANSVERSAL)","guid":"eTNZ5Zo9RxW0gCrMMdOGeg","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"Farmacocinetica\\Nalterada","guid":"DeusM3w3hAaVsQ4LBy6AKw","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"Clearance renal disminuido → ajustar dosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"VFG siempre antes de prescribir","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"150","text":"Fluoroquinolonas: MAYOR riesgo tendinopatia, QTc, delirium","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"149","text":"Interacciones\\Nfarmacologicas","guid":"uOsenw0GujWiSN_VOECEMw","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"Macrolidos + estatinas → rabdomiolisis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"Macrolidos + antiarritmicos → QTc prolongado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"154","text":"Fluoroquinolonas + corticoides → tendon ruptura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"154","text":"Metronidazol + warfarina → potencia efecto","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"149","text":"Fragilidad y\\Npolifarmacia","guid":"U7BknC6M7xFqUtIw9zKzIw","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"Start low, go slow → pero no go nowhere","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"Evaluar riesgo/beneficio individualizado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"Deprescripcion post-tratamiento → revisar lista actualizada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"149","text":"Delirium por\\NATB","guid":"4yp3QY9YSm98KaOizqQrjg","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"Fluoroquinolonas → riesgo neurotoxicidad/delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"Metronidazol → neurotoxicidad en uso prolongado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"163","text":"Preferir betalactamicos cuando sea posible","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClinicas","guid":"Y4UCE8oiQP5N3ztC3R-mQQ","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"Sinusitis aguda + alergia PNC tipo 1 → levofloxacino o moxifloxacino (costo-efectivo en Chile)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"Cefuroxima/cefpodoxima: alternativa teorica pero ~$60.000/caja → barrera economica real","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"167","text":"Azitromicina NO es primera linea en sinusitis aguda → resistencia ~30%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"167","text":"Azitromicina a dosis baja prolongada → RSC SIN polipos (inmunomodulacion, no ATB)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"167","text":"RSC CON polipos → corticoides +/- biologicos +/- cirugia, NO macrolidos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"167","text":"100% S. pyogenes sensible a penicilina → SIEMPRE primera linea en faringitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"167","text":"Otitis externa maligna: sospechar en AM + DM2 con otalgia intensa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"167","text":"Evitar fluoroquinolonas en AM fragil: tendinopatia, delirium, QTc","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"167","text":"NO ATB en: resfrio comun, faringitis no estreptococica, laringitis, bronquitis aguda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"167","text":"Metronidazol complementa bien los betalactamicos en infecciones mixtas ORL","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"0","text":"VER\\NTAMBIEN","guid":"9zZhD8j2nBtGkuVvv490-Q","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"→ Rinosinusitis (ORL)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"→ Otitis (ORL)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"178","text":"→ Faringitis estreptococica (Infectologia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"178","text":"→ Delirium (Geriatria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"178","text":"→ Polifarmacia y deprescripcion (Geriatria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"178","text":"→ Fragilidad (Valoracion Geriatrica)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"1. Chow AW et al. IDSA Clinical Practice Guideline for Acute Bacterial Rhinosinusitis. Clin Infect Dis. 2012;54(8):e72-e112.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"2. Rosenfeld RM et al. Clinical Practice Guideline (Update): Adult Sinusitis. Otolaryngol Head Neck Surg. 2015;152(2 Suppl):S1-S39.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"185","text":"3. Shulman ST et al. IDSA Guideline for Diagnosis and Management of GAS Pharyngitis. Clin Infect Dis. 2012;55(10):e86-102.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"185","text":"4. Lieberthal AS et al. Diagnosis and Management of Acute Otitis Media. Pediatrics. 2013;131(3):e964-99.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"185","text":"5. Fokkens WJ et al. EPOS 2020: European Position Paper on Rhinosinusitis and Nasal Polyps. Rhinology. 2020;58(Suppl S29):1-464.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"185","text":"6. Cohen R. Antimicrobial Treatment of ENT Infections. Arch Pediatr. 2017;24(12S):S9-S16.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"185","text":"7. Brook I. Microbiology and Management of Deep Neck Infections and Lemierre Syndrome. ORL J Otorhinolaryngol. 2003;65(2):117-20.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"185","text":"8. AAO-HNS Pocket Guide to Antimicrobial Therapy in Otolaryngology. 2024.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"185","text":"9. FDA Drug Safety Communication: Fluoroquinolone Antibacterial Drugs. 2016.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"185","text":"10. Harris AM et al. Appropriate Antibiotic Use for Acute RTI in Adults. Ann Intern Med. 2016;164(6):425-35.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":195,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"ORL","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología","filename":"ATB Patologias ORL iPad","id":"map_1555","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"ATB Patologias ORL iPad"}